WEBVTT


1
00:00:00.940 --> 00:00:02.040
What’s up, everybody?

2
00:00:02.860 --> 00:00:03.820
If you are watching this video,

3
00:00:03.820 --> 00:00:05.400
Deus ETH is over.

4
00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:08.140
It was a small showcase of a brand new experience

5
00:00:08.140 --> 00:00:10.620
that is now accessible, thanks to blockchain technology.

6
00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:13.780
Our show was announced on the 19th of February,

7
00:00:13.780 --> 00:00:16.540
and we have sold 50 unique hand made characters

8
00:00:16.540 --> 00:00:19.040
for 0.3 ETH each.

9
00:00:19.040 --> 00:00:22.608
According to our storyline, 50 heroes were wandering in the desert

10
00:00:22.608 --> 00:00:24.660
in search of the promised land.

11
00:00:25.740 --> 00:00:27.280
Heroes die during the show,

12
00:00:27.380 --> 00:00:30.380
and 3 survivors share the box office in the end.

13
00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:35.340
The Deus audience could not only watch the dramatic plot twists in the show,

14
00:00:35.340 --> 00:00:37.620
but they could also trade their characters

15
00:00:37.620 --> 00:00:38.800
and make some profit.

16
00:00:38.809 --> 00:00:41.510
We call it “a post-internet theater”.

17
00:00:41.510 --> 00:00:43.789
The entertainment of value.

18
00:00:43.789 --> 00:00:45.240
There are more shows to come!

19
00:00:45.449 --> 00:00:48.880
Sport shows, reality shows, games, etc.

20
00:00:48.890 --> 00:00:51.480
Tokenville will become a sort of a Hollywood studio

21
00:00:51.480 --> 00:00:54.020
that will produce and distribute content.

22
00:00:54.020 --> 00:00:57.080
So, we wanna welcome you in Tokenville!

23
00:00:57.080 --> 00:00:58.940
Make yourself at home.